HEADWORD: Syndetical
<hw>Syn*det"ic*al</hw>
<pr>(?)</pr>, }</mhw> <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[Gr. <?/, from <?/ to bind
together; <grk>sy`n</grk> with + <?/ to bind; cf.
<er>Asyndetic</er>.]</ety> <def>Connecting; conjunctive; <as>as,
